room_title: Escape room "221B Baker Street" by Escape Lincoln in Lincoln
review: Went for a friend's birthday. Had a lot of fun working out puzzles and was super impressed with the creative room. We did the Poe (as in Edgar Allen) room and it had a great moody/gloomy feel which felt perfect for the theme.

room_title: Escape room "221B Baker Street" by Escape Lincoln in Lincoln
review: I did the Poe room, and I think it's my favorite escape room to date! I would love the opportunity to check out their other rooms!

room_title: Escape room "221B Baker Street" by Escape Lincoln in Lincoln
review: Really fun! We did Poe and it was perfect for our group of four.
